Lines.Comment: I should be getting rid of people like you.
I am accustomed to the ways of mercenaries and adventurers. I have some gold around here... uhm, uh, a blue item at least.
Think you can train me in the ways of the Sword? I'm... still getting accustomed to mine.
<laugh> I believe I like you. How unexpected.
The terrans? Oh, were there no viable allies?
If you can't take the heat, get outta the kitchen.
Nice! Someone with real combat training.
Must I yet again cooperate with mortal heroes? Do you have the valor necessary to purge this realm of evil? I am watching you, "hero." Try not to disappoint me.
Do you know not the dragon queen?
Seek justice, young one. Vengeance, if you must. But do not abandon hope.
Uh, no... You must be thinking of the OTHER heavy metal bull... Gotta go!
End your prattle. We have a fight to win.
